## Do Not
- Do NOT skip updating CHANGELOG.md.
- Do NOT increment YY on dev changes (deployment bumps YY, not ZZ).
- Do NOT change the 1.0 prefix unless explicitly requested by the user.
- Do NOT use vague descriptions like "refactored" without stating what changed from X to Y.
